          Zimbabwe's premier news aggregation platform delivering comprehensive local and regional coverage. 
          Real-time updates, verified sources, and intelligent content curation for informed citizens.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <a href="https://hararemetro.co.zw" target="_blank" class="btn-marketing-primary">
